snippet.title: PAC-MAN COMMUNITY Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you part of the PAC-MAN COMMUNITY yet? Team up in squads of 4 players to dominate ghosts, eat pellets, and climb the leaderboards! Play now at fb.gg/play/pacmancommunity
